<div class="artist-section">
	<div class="artist-wrapper">
		<span class="header-emoji">ðŸ¤”</span>
		<h1>How big of a fan <br><span>are you really?</span></h1>
		<p class="intro-p">Find out by listening to a short snippet and try to identify the song.</p>
		<span class="subline">Pick your artist</span>
		<input type="text" class="search" autofocus aria-label="search spotify for an artist" placeholder="Search for an artist"/>
		<div class="artists-container"></div>
	</div>
